Customize the Supervisor Experience

To enhance how supervisors interact with agents, customers, and your contact center, customize Omni Supervisor. Because Omni Supervisor supports multiple channel types, your customizations can impact the supervisor experience for other channel types.

Customize Omni Supervisor for Voice

At this point, you've already enabled Omni Supervisor. Now it's time to customize Omni Supervisor to meet your needs. For example, enable supervisors to change agents’ queues and skills. Add actions to the Omni Supervisor tabs. Set up a supervisor configuration to change what a group of supervisors sees in Omni Supervisor. Add Omni Supervisor where supervisors work—in a Lightning app.

Enable Listen In for Supervisors

Enable supervisors to listen in to any ongoing call from Omni Supervisor.
title: Customizing Supervisor Experience
